  "text": "A measure of food-web 'shape'; high values are more triangular, low values are more 'square' in shape. When <1 the food web has an inverted structure that might indicate instability. Note criticisms of this attribute [CITATION_1] and its sensitivity to the common practice of aggregating of low trophic level taxa.",
